VIM MASTERCLASS NOTES:

(do not use caps locks in vim... kek)

Navigation:

BY WORD -> w W b B -> moving around by word 
LINE -> (end)$  (start)^
DOWN PAGE -> ctrl-f
UP PAGE -> ctrl-b




Interface: 

NUMBERED LINES -> :set nu 
RULER -> :set ruler!


Deleting text:

d + motion -> delete everything in path of motion

e.g. dw, d3w, d0, d$, dG

DOT (.) -> repeats previous command


